"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797612","Department for Education","false","2017-12-04","<p>Following publication of the Early Years Workforce Strategy, we have set up a task and finish group of early years sector stakeholders to consider gender diversity in the sector in more depth. The group is in its early stages and more information will be available as work progresses.</p>","Scarborough and Whitby","Mr Robert Goodwill",,"2017-12-04T16:26:37.973Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797612/answer","Biography information for Mr Robert Goodwill","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797612/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797612/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2017-11-29","Pre-school Education: Recruitment","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, whether her Department has a strategy to increase the proportion of male employees in the early years sector.","false","Biography information for Tracy Brabin","Batley and Spen","Tracy Brabin","116575"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797613","Department for Education","false","2017-12-04","<p>I am unable to reveal the names of academies awaiting transfer to another trust. We are committed to transparency, but this should not undermine the process of rebrokering by exacerbating any uncertainty. Where transfers do happen, these are announced as soon as possible and when appropriate, so that transfers can happen smoothly and in the best interests of pupils.</p>","Scarborough and Whitby","Mr Robert Goodwill",,"2017-12-04T17:26:52.427Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797613/answer","Biography information for Mr Robert Goodwill","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797613/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/797613/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2017-11-29","Academies","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, which academies in England are currently awaiting a transfer to another trust.","false","Biography information for Angela Rayner","Ashton-under-Lyne","Angela Rayner","116576"
